parameters: Welcome to Elmo Village! Where did you ladies come from?

Our specialty is called Chao Roast, which is a sautéed dish
with pork and mushrooms. You should try eating it while
you're here!

There was a pervert who loved mushrooms in the past... They
researched mushrooms so much that it became a local
specialty. But as a result, they ended up being poisoned...

It's about time to replace this ship... But I still want to
sail with you... Partner...

Somehow, when I feel refreshed, I start to not care about my
worries anymore... Alright, maybe I should just throw
everything away and go on a journey...

A little while ago, you know. Some girls moved in from
outside. I immediately became their friend! Isn't that
impressive?!

This village, there's nothing here, right? I'm a little torn
about whether to go to Yurisene or not. But leaving my
father behind... I don't know. Hey, what do you think?

That's true. But, it's only one life, you know... I kind of
want to be surrounded by handsome guys in the city....

City Mount...!!? How dare you! There are plenty of good
places even in this countryside!!
It's an old doghouse. It seems to be well taken care of...
